If the view as a control with id = scan, then this control will get
initial focus. All pages which use this layout must ensure that the script PieceReplenish.partial.js is included.
*@
@model DcmsMobile.PieceReplenish.ViewModels.ViewModelBase
<!DOCTYPE html>
<!--
